sql:
SELECT product_size_id, stock_quantity
FROM product_sizes
WHERE stock_quantity > 0;

external_knowledge:
- Completed orders are considered sold and thus, contribute to the revenue and quantity sold; 
- Total revenue is the sum of the product of quantity and unit price for each order item; 
- Product-size combinations with zero sales are excluded to focus on actively sold products.

